---
---

<section class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[1280px] border-x border-[color:var(--color-border)]">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-16 border-b border-[color:var(--color-border)] px-4 py-20 md:px-10 md:py-28">

    <div data-reveal>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-medium sm:text-3xl lg:text-[40px] tracking-tight">
        Proof in Practice
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-md text-base font-light text-[color:var(--color-ink-secondary)]">
        Bold claims are easy. Real results are harder. Here's what GTM teams actually say.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="columns-1 gap-5 sm:columns-2 lg:columns-3" data-reveal>
      {[
        {
          text: "The social listening agent and AI reply agent are perfect for our GTM motions. They efficiently help us book 20+ meetings monthly without any manual prospecting.",
          name: "Santosh Patil",
          handle: "@santoshpatil",
          role: "CEO",
          init: "SP",
          bg: "bg-green-100",
          txt: "text-green-700",
        },
        {
          text: "Typpout feels different, it's built for PMMs and GTM teams, not just sales. The ICP Finder alone saves me hours every week. I stopped using Apollo entirely.",
          name: "Raiyaan Akhtar",
          handle: "@raiyaan_gtm",
          role: "GTM Lead, Carpl.AI",
          init: "RA",
          bg: "bg-blue-100",
          txt: "text-blue-700",
        },
        {
          text: "Instead of juggling 4-5 different tools, my team now finds ICPs, generates content, and runs outreach in one place. We booked 10 qualified meetings in the first two weeks.",
          name: "Swapnil",
          handle: "@swapnil_mktg",
          role: "CEO, DigiMatrix Marketing",
          init: "SW",
          bg: "bg-pink-100",
          txt: "text-pink-700",
        },
        {
          text: "Speed matters. Typpout helped us move from idea to pipeline in days. The AI outreach felt personal, we closed our first 3 customers directly from campaigns.",
          name: "Sanskar Pitta",
          handle: "@sanskarpitta",
          role: "Netmetschek Group",
          init: "SK",
          bg: "bg-yellow-100",
          txt: "text-yellow-700",
        },
        {
          text: "We were spending 3 hours a day manually monitoring LinkedIn. Typpout cut that to zero and the quality of leads went up. The ICP matching is genuinely impressive.",
          name: "Priya Mehta",
          handle: "@priyamehta_rev",
          role: "Head of Revenue",
          init: "PM",
          bg: "bg-purple-100",
          txt: "text-purple-700",
        },
        {
          text: "Our reply rate jumped from 12% to 47% within the first month. The AI replies are fast and on-brand, prospects can't even tell it's automated until they're already on the calendar.",
          name: "James Okafor",
          handle: "@jamesokafor",
          role: "VP Sales, Growthbase",
          init: "JO",
          bg: "bg-orange-100",
          txt: "text-orange-700",
        },
        {
          text: "I was skeptical about AI outreach tools but Typpout actually delivers. It picked up a competitor switch signal on X and booked a demo before we even knew the prospect existed.",
          name: "Lauren Park",
          handle: "@laurenpark_gtm",
          role: "Demand Gen Manager",
          init: "LP",
          bg: "bg-indigo-100",
          txt: "text-indigo-700",
        },
        {
          text: "Finally a GTM tool that doesn't feel like it was designed for a 100-person sales team. Perfect for our lean 3-person GTM team. We punch way above our weight now.",
          name: "Marcus Webb",
          handle: "@marcuswebb",
          role: "Founder, Synthos",
          init: "MW",
          bg: "bg-teal-100",
          txt: "text-teal-700",
        },
        {
          text: "The funding signal detection is a game changer. We get notified within minutes when a target account closes a round, and the outreach goes out while the news is still fresh.",
          name: "Divya Rao",
          handle: "@divyarao_sales",
          role: "Sales Director",
          init: "DR",
          bg: "bg-rose-100",
          txt: "text-rose-700",
        },
      ].map((t) => (
        <div class="mb-5 break-inside-avoid rounded-2xl border border-[color:var(--color-border)] bg-white p-5">
          <!-- X/Twitter icon -->
          <div class="mb-3 flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
              <span class:list={["grid h-8 w-8 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-full text-[11px] font-semibold", t.bg, t.txt]}>{t.init}</span>
              <div>
                <div class="text-[13px] font-medium text-[color:var(--color-ink)]">{t.name}</div>
                <div class="text-[11px] text-[color:var(--color-ink-muted)]">{t.handle}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-[color:var(--color-ink-subtle)]" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-4.714-6.231-5.401 6.231H2.738l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.253 5.622zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-[color:var(--color-ink-strong)]">{t.text}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
